msg.msgText: A call to unsubscribe() from client {1} for subscription {0} failed because there are active consumers of the subscription, or a session is still using messages from the subscription.

msgExplanation.p: The unsubscribe() method can succeed only if the subscription is no longer in use.

msgUserResponse.p: Ensure that all consumer objects have been closed and all messages and transactions complete before calling unsubscribe().
